values for the latter shown in <xref ref-type="fig" rid="awt263-F4">Fig. 4</xref>. Regional BP<sub>ND</sub> values pooled across all subjects are shown in <xref ref-type="table" rid="awt263-T3">Table 3</xref>. BP<sub>ND</sub> values on placebo were in the same range as those previously reported in a study examining test&#x02013;retest variability of baseline <sup>18</sup>F-fallypride BP<sub>ND</sub> across the same brain regions (<xref rid="awt263-B21" ref-type="bibr">Cropley <italic>et al.</italic>, 2008</xref>) (<ext-link ext-link-type="uri" xlink:href="http://brain.oxfordjournals.org/lookup/suppl/doi:10.1093/brain/awt263/-/DC1">Supplementary material</ext-link>).
